text: Motion
Motion
Motion
Motion

The interlude's turn,
feels like it's a bit long, so I wait...

I'm looking at Chiyuki-san,
trying to sync up the timing...

─Tenka, sorry for making you wait.
My apologies.

Ah...
Producer-san...!

No, wasn't waiting...!
Tenka, was writing in my notebook...

Ah, I see. That's good.
Is that homework?

Ah... no, it's not...
Was making a lesson notebook for Naa-chan...!

Because Naa-chan's foot hurts,
so she can't participate in the lesson yet...

Is that so...!
You're so kind, Tenka.
Hehe...

Naa-chan always...
ends up helping all the time...

And Naa-chan...
is looking forward to the unit live too...

Things she can do,
as Tenka...
Yeah, that's right.

─Alright! For such a kind Tenka, I'll treat you
to anything you like. Order as much as you want.

Eh...!
Really...? Yay...!

Hehe...
Tenka wanna eat pizza... and parfait too...!
What should I choose...?
